                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18490226-747-offence-1 t18490226-name-784"></join>Hannah Solomons</persName>, and stealing 2 gowns, 1 time-piece, 2 salt-cellars, and 1 pair of stockings, value 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; I half-crown, and other moneys; her property. <persName id="t18490226-name-785" type="judiciaryName">
                        <interp inst="t18490226-name-785" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
